eventsArray.name: Coding Junction Induction Event
eventsArray.desc: This is the first event organised by the Coding Junction Club. We welcome all the members to our new club. We are trying to build an active community of young coders with passion and energy for the Coding and Programming. We will provide a unique platform for all the brilliant minds and making their vision and belief into a success. This event is to reach to all the new comers and expand our new club.

eventsArray.name: Sparks Contest
eventsArray.desc: 1. Unleash and showcase your photos with the new sparks contest. 2. All notifications regarding the club in one spot. 3. Seamless interaction with club members. 4. Efficiently express opinions with polls.
